CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

May 9, 2005

[Cite as 05/09/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-2240.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2004-1464. State v. Anthony.

Hamilton App. No. C-030510, 2004-Ohio-3894. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County.

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that the case is dismissed as moot. Oral argument in this case, currently scheduled for May 11, 2005, is cancelled.
